  "description": [
    "CDR J W Kelsey Jr New Executive Officer Takes Station Post CDR John W Kelsey Jr has assumed the duties of Naval Sta tion Executive Officer He re lieved CDR Raymond VV Lamka on 16 April CDR Lamka who took over thi Executive Officer duties on 13 October 1960 was relieved be cause of illness CDR Kelsey has served as the Naval Station Act ing Executive Officer since 17 Feb this year Prior to CDR Lamka s illness CDR Kelsey had served as the Naval Stations Operations Officer CDR Kelsey brings 20 years of naval experience to his new post a major portion of it served in submarines Sea Commands Included in CDR Kelseys sea commands is that of Command ing Officer of the submarines USS Aspro USS Sterlet and USS Be sugo He also served as Executive Officer in the submarines USS Halfbeak and USS Cabezon His sea duty also includes that of navigator in USS S48 and USS Dolphin and engineering officer in USS Irex Other highlights of his career Continued on Page 6 Column 2 COLORS TO GUIDON OCS Class 58 Color Giri Mis Vlctoire C Griffin attaches streamer to A Companys guidon Ml Griffin a ph"
